title: Klaada
description: Traveling through the vast world of ideas in his ark made of thoughts, Klaada decided to create bridges with an intention to connect the two worlds. This bridges are made of sound, and they transport people on the other side of the mirror, connecting them with implicit order which is the base of everything that exists. Working on dismantlement of cerebral reduction vents, Klaada creates music based on both ancient and contemporary inspiration, making a symbiosis of consonant, dissonant, organic and digital. His opus consists out of two psychedelic downtempo albums (Breaking the Cycle, Antipodes of the Self-Conscious Mind), psytrance EP (Underground Gathering), couple of remixes and singles and bunch of non released material. Bavimo se uvozom i distribucijom sadnog materijala vocnih i dekorativnih vrsta kao i uslugama u hortikulturi i vocarstvu. Poslujemo od 2012. god. a sadni materijal koji isporucujemo nabavljamo od renomiranih proizvodjaca iz EU i dr. kontinenata. Nas tim cine mladi i perspektivni strucni ljudi iz svijeta agronomije, agroekonomije, hortikulture, ekonomije i prava. Trudimo se pratiti trendove u Evropi i svijetu i donijeti u nas region sve sto smatramo da vrijedi i da ima perspektivu pa tako posljednjih godina nase najprodavanije vocne vrste su kalemljeni orah lateralno rodnih sorti iz Turske, Americka i Ruska borovnica kao i mnoge druge. Ako ste u dilemi i zelite zasnovati plantazu javite nam se, pokusat cemo naci nakbolje rjesenje za Vas, jer Vase zadovoljstvo je nas uspjeh! Vas siguran partner za sadnju! NET GREEN GROUP

title: garethtrooper
description: Hello and welcome to my YouTube channel. I'm amateur transport enthusiast from Croatia and this is my hobby channel. I travel around Croatia and Europe and I film transport, mostly trams and other transport vehicles such as trains, buses, funiculars... Also You can find some different videos like travel videos, storm reports, model and garden railways, emergency vehicles... The great majority of videos I have made and only a part of footage was made by my collaborators from different European countries. I like to travel, but I can't travel to every town and country so I decided to collabrate with some interesting transport YouTubers. I do uploads everyday, only in time of lockdown I have uploaded a two times per week. I hope that I could travel again like before, so the videos from different cities and countries will be on my channel. I film with my mobile phones, so sorry if quality of some videos isn't high. I wish You a good and quality time spent here on my channel.
